data.description: Wow!!! Seller has spared no expense in updating this 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom airy & spacious Villa. You will find Taj Mahal Quartzite coutertops in kitchen. New stainless steal appliances, Custom shaker wood cabinetry, soft closing with pullout draws in Kitchen, dinning room, hallway and bathrooms not to mention new flooring throughout home!!. Large living room for entertaining and additional space with your enclosed Veranda,and just beond that, you have a open patio of a peaceful view, overing the conservation area. Master bedroom features a custom walk-in closet with plenty of shevling & an amazing ensuite with custom cabinets, pullout draws and granite counter top, New comfort high toliet & new sink. A Large walk-in lipless base shower. Main Bathroom also has new comfort high toilets, custom cabinet with a new sink and Taj mahal quartzite top. Sellers have added extra concrete to driveway and walkways for a wider path from car to home. Timber Pines is a 55+ gated adult community with 4 Golf Courses, Award Winning Pickle Ball Center, New State of the Art Wellness Center, Tennis, Club House and Restaurant, Performing Arts Center, Residents Activity Center, 2 Geothermal Pools, Billiards, Bocce, Wood Shop, Arts and Crafts, Paws Park for your pets, Over 100 Clubs, Cable TV, 2 boxes and highest speed internet included in HOA fee.
